snippet.title: Science secrets of the scariest haunted houses
snippet.description: ScareHouse taps into neuroscience to take the experience from spooky to psychological thriller. Some visitors get so freaked they end up using their safe word.

snippet.title: Alcatel One Touch Evo
snippet.description: The 8-inch tablet starts at $299 and features a LED flashing flip-cover, but otherwise lacks any excitement.

snippet.title: Zuckerberg buys four new houses for, um, privacy
snippet.description: The Facebook CEO purchases four residences adjacent to his existing home. He's said to have reacted to a developer's plans to buy one of the houses and sell it as "the one next door to Zuckerberg."

snippet.title: Google Doodle houses Jane Addams tribute
snippet.description: Today's doodle points to the accomplishments of Hull-House founder Jane Addams, a pioneer and leader in areas ranging from social work to women's suffrage to the quest for world peace.

snippet.title: Nvidia's 'Tegra Tab' houses unreleased Tegra 4 and stylus
snippet.description: The unconfirmed 7-inch tablet is expected to feature a previously unreleased Tegra 4 variant and stylus capabilities.

snippet.title: Hottest holiday gifts unboxed
snippet.description: Check out some of our favorite tech picks, right out of the box.

snippet.title: Holiday deal roundup
snippet.description: It's time to deal so check back often to see what the latest offers are. But don't wait; many of these are limited-time and limited-quantity offers. And if you see a deal that you feel is worthy, drop us a note and we'll do our best to add it to the list.

snippet.title: Prime was prime, as Amazon reports another record holiday
snippet.description: Although UPS delays left some Amazon customers empty-handed, the company boasts a merry Christmas, both for sales and services like its Amazon Prime.

snippet.title: Acer's Iconia W4 houses Windows 8.1 in an 8-inch $299 package (pictures)
snippet.description: The Iconia W4 from Acer is the followup to the badly received Iconia W3 from earlier this year.
